IntelÂŽ IXGBE driver
===================

This directory contains source code of FreeBSD ixgbe driver generated on
2024-08-38 released by the team which develops
basic drivers for any ixgbe NIC. The sub-directory of base/
contains the original source package.
This driver is valid for the product(s) listed below

* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit AF DA Dual Port Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit AT Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit AT2 Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit CX4 Dual Port Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit XF LR Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit XF SR Dual Port Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 10 Gigabit XF SR Server Adapter
* IntelÂŽ 82598 10 Gigabit Ethernet Controller
* IntelÂŽ 82599 10 Gigabit Ethernet Controller
* IntelÂŽ Ethernet Controller X540-AT2
* IntelÂŽ Ethernet Server Adapter X520 Series
* IntelÂŽ Ethernet Server Adapter X520-T2
* IntelÂŽ Ethernet Controller X550 Series
* IntelÂŽ Ethernet Controller E610 Series

Updating the driver
===================

NOTE: The source code in this directory should not be modified apart from
the following file(s):

    ixgbe_osdep.h
    ixgbe_osdep.c
